    • defaultPrecision

      public static int defaultPrecision​(DataType dataType)
      Returns the precision of the field

      Precision is the specified column size. For numeric data, this is the maximum precision. For character data, this is the length in characters. For datetime datatypes, this is the length in characters of the String representation (assuming the maximum allowed defaultPrecision of the fractional seconds component).
